aholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><div class=\'shareaholic-like-buttonset\' style=\'float:none;height:30px;\'><a class=\'shareaholic-fblike\' data-shr_layout=\'button_count\' data-shr_showfaces=\'false\' data-shr_href=\'http%3A%2F%2Fajaydsouza.com%2Farchives%2F2012%2F04%2F01%2Fnew-wordpress-plugin-add-to-all%2F\' data-shr_title=\'%5BNew+WordPress+Plugin%5D+Add+to+All\'></a><a class=\'shareaholic-fbsend\' data-shr_href=\'http%3A%2F%2Fajaydsouza.com%2Farchives%2F2012%2F04%2F01%2Fnew-wordpress-plugin-add-to-all%2F\'></a><a class=\'shareaholic-googleplusone\' data-shr_size=\'medium\' data-shr_count=\'true\' data-shr_href=\'http%3A%2F%2Fajaydsouza.com%2Farchives%2F2012%2F04%2F01%2Fnew-wordpress-plugin-add-to-all%2F\' data-shr_title=\'%5BNew+WordPress+Plugin%5D+Add+to+All\'></a><a class=\'shareaholic-tweetbutton\' data-shr_count=\'horizontal\' data-shr_href=\'http%3A%2F%2Fajaydsouza.com%2Farchives%2F2012%2F04%2F01%2Fnew-wordpress-plugin-add-to-all%2F\' data-shr_title=\'%5BNew+WordPress+Plugin%5D+Add+to+All\'></a></div><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><p><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/add-to-all/">Add to All</a> is a powerful plugin that will allow you to add custom code or CSS to your header, footer, content or feed.</p>\n<p><img style="background-image: none; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; padding-top: 0px; border: 0px;" title="WordPress Plugin Add to All" src="http://ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/wordpress-logo-notext-bg.png" alt="WordPress Plugin Add to All" width="111" height="111" border="0" /></p>\n<p>Add to All comes with out of the box support for Google Analytics, Statcounter, Kontera, with other third party services in the pipeline.</p>\n<p>With this plugin installed, you do not need to edit your theme files every time you switch themes. You can also add custom CSS styles to your header as well as any HTML code to the header or footer of the theme.</p>\n<p>The plugin gives you the power to add content to your feed in addition to adding a copyright notice. This is especially useful if you have any website scraping your feeds.</p>\n<p><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/add-to-all/">Visit product info page »</a></p>\n<div id="crp_related"><h4>Related Posts:</h4><ul><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2012/04/19/add-to-all-v1-0-1-and-better-search-1-2-1/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Add to All v1.0.1 and Better Search 1.2.1</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2009/03/08/new-wordpress-plugin-add-to-footer/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">New WordPress Plugin: Add to Footer</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2008/11/30/wordpress-plugin-add-to-feed/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">WordPress Plugin: Add to Feed</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2008/12/20/add-to-feed-wordpress-plugin-updated-to-v11/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Add to Feed WordPress Plugin updated to v1.1</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2010/12/01/review-idrive-online-backup/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Review: Idrive Online Backup</a></li><li>Powered by <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/contextual-related-posts/">Contextual Related Posts</a></li></ul></div><div class="shr-publisher-2033"></div><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><hr style="border-top:black solid 1px" /><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2012/04/01/new-wordpress-plugin-add-to-all/">[New WordPress Plugin] Add to All</a> was first posted on April 1, 2012 at 7:23 pm.<br />© 2003-2009 "<a href="http://ajaydsouza.com">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>". Use of this feed is for personal non-commercial use only. If you are not reading this article in your feed reader, then the s