-shr_count=\'horizontal\' data-shr_href=\'http%3A%2F%2Fajaydsouza.com%2Farchives%2F2012%2F03%2F23%2Ftop-10-v1-8-1-and-contextual-related-posts-v1-7-1%2F\' data-shr_title=\'Top+10+v1.8.1+and+Contextual+Related+Posts+v1.7.1\'></a></div><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><p>About 2 weeks back I released a minor update to <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/top-10/">Top 10</a>. This is a minor update that fixes the links in the Dashboard widgets when you login to your WP-Admin.</p>\n<p>I have been working on an update for <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/contextual-related-posts/">Contextual Related Posts</a> to incorporate some of the changes in Top 10, especially related to thumbnail support. A summary of changes in v1.7 and 1.7.1 are:</p>\n<h5>1.7.1</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Minor bug fix for location of thumbnail</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>1.7</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: New function <code>related posts()</code> that allows you to manually add posts to your theme</li>\n<li>Added: Support for <a href="https://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/video-thumbnails/">Video Thumbnails</a> plugin</li>\n<li>Added: Thumbnail settings now reflect max width and max height instead of fixed width and height</li>\n<li>Added: Option to display thumbnails before or after the title</li>\n<li>Added: Option to not display thumbnails instead of the default thumbnail</li>\n<li>Added: Plugin now uses InnoDB instead of MyISAM if your server is running mySQL v5.6 or higher</li>\n<li>Modified: Cleaner Settings page interface</li>\n<li>Modified: Updated <a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/contextual-related-posts/faq/">FAQ page</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>This update is the first step towards adding in better support for styling the list, which has been the biggest request from most users of the plugin.</p>\n<p>I have also added a <a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/contextual-related-posts/other_notes/">wishlist</a> for features I would like to add in future versions. As usual, suggestions and feature requests are welcome and will be implemented as soon as practicable.</p>\n<div id="crp_related"><h4>Related Posts:</h4><ul><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2011/12/25/merry-christmas-and-happy-top-10-v1-8/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Merry Christmas and Happy Top 10 v1.8</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2009/12/24/contextual-related-posts-v1-5-1-with-post-thumbnail-support/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Contextual Related Posts v1.5.1 with Post Thumbnail support</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2009/08/02/update-to-contextual-related-posts/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Update to Contextual Related Posts</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2011/10/08/contextual-related-posts-v1-6-5/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Contextual Related Posts v1.6.5</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2009/08/09/contextual-related-posts-v1-4-2-released/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Contextual Related Posts v1.4.2 released</a></li><li>Powered by <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/contextual-related-posts/">Contextual Related Posts</a></li></ul></div><div class="shr-publisher-2026"></div><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><hr style="border-top:black solid 1px" /><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2012/03/23/top-10-v1-8-1-and-contextual-related-posts-v1-7-1/">Top 10 v1.8.1 and Contextual Related Posts v1.7.1</a> was first posted on March 23, 2012 at 8:15 am.<br />© 2003-2009 "<a href="http://ajaydsouza.com">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>". Use of this feed is for personal non-commercial use only. If you are not reading this article in your feed reader, then the site is guilty of copyright infringement. Please <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/contact/">contact me</a>.<br /><br /><s