a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/contextual-related-posts/">Contextual Related Posts</a>.</p>\n<blockquote><p>Display a list of contextually related posts for the current post. You can select the number of posts to display and if you want to automatically display the related posts in your content / feed.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Changes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Few code tweaks to optimise mySQL performance </li>\n<li>Added: Dutch and Spanish language files </li>\n</ul>\n<p>The mySQL tweaks are courtesy <a href="http://profiles.wordpress.org/users/DH-Shredder/">Mike Schroder</a>, who contacted me with some key ways to optimise the mySQL query lookups. With these changes, the plugin should be a lot lighter on your mySQL databases especially if you got tonnes of posts and content.</p>\n<p>I have also added in the Dutch and Spanish translations to this release. The current set of translations include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Danish by <a href="http://blogos.dk">Team Blogos</a> </li>\n<li>Dutch by <a href="http://wpwebshop.com/">WPwebshop</a> </li>\n<li>Italian by <a href="http://gidibao.net/">Gianni</a> </li>\n<li>Spanish by <a href="http://oardesign.com.ar">Octavio</a> </li>\n</ul>\n<p>Read more about <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/contextual-related-posts/">Contextual Related Posts »</a></p>\n<div id="crp_related"><h4>Related Posts:</h4><ul><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2009/08/09/contextual-related-posts-v1-4-2-released/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Contextual Related Posts v1.4.2 released</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2009/08/02/update-to-contextual-related-posts/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Update to Contextual Related Posts</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2009/03/09/contextual-related-posts-bug-fix-release/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Contextual Related Posts &#8211; Bug fix release</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2010/01/19/contextual-related-posts-v1-