2Fajaydsouza.com%2Farchives%2F2011%2F08%2F17%2Ftop-v1-7%2F\' data-shr_title=\'Top+v1.7\'></a></div><div style="clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;"></div><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><p>After a long long time, I have updated my plugin <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/top-10/">Top 10</a>. The plugin is a powerful way to track daily and total visits on your blog posts and display the count as well as popular posts.</p>\n<p>v1.7 is a much needed updated at includes better support for WordPress 3.x. Main changes include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Excludes posts in the top lists from select categories </li>\n<li>Modified: Performance improvements </li>\n<li>Modified: Better compatibility with the latest versions of WordPress. If you are using the sidebar widgets, please re-add them to your theme under Appearance &gt; Widgets </li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have been using an older version of the plugin, I suggest upgrading to v1.7 mainly due to the performance improvements. I have a few updates that I&#8217;d like to test out to improve performance still further, especially on heavy traffic blogs.</p>\n<p>There are also several features that I intend to add in as time permits.</p>\n<p>If you are already a user of the plugin, you can upgrade it directly from your Plugins page in WP-Admin.</p>\n<p class="downloads"><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/top-10/">Read more and download Top 10</a></p>\n<div id="crp_related"><h4>Related Posts:</h4><ul><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2009/03/04/top-10-plugin-now-tracking-daily-popular-posts/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Top 10 Plugin: Now tracking Daily Popular Posts</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2009/02/17/top-10-v11-released/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">Top 10 v1.1 Released</a></li><li><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2011/08/22/twittercounter-v1-5/" rel="bookmark" class="crp_title">TwitterCounter v1.5</a></li><li><a h