INSERT INTO `til_posts` VALUES (5, 1, '2012-04-22 04:58:15', '2012-04-22 04:58:15', '<blockquote>\r\n<h5>Update: starting to share more.. lots of emotion to organize..</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>child|adult mental health advocacy (like <a title="Missing Matters" href="https://www.facebook.com/prosody/posts/533138483380684">"Missing Matters" rhymes</a>) and emotional-verbal-physical abuse survivor thoughts (like <a title="g.c\'s answer to Telling on long-lost-and-profound abuse" href="http://www.quora.com/Abuse-Survivors/Should-a-survivor-of-childhood-sexual-abuse-tell-on-the-abuser-even-if-it-happened-a-long-time-ago/answer/Gabriell-Gaston-Croft">my answer about long-lost-and-profound pain and abuse</a> and <a title="gabriell context(e\'s answers about Abuse Survivors" href="http://www.quora.com/Gabriell-Gaston-Croft/answers/Abuse-Survivors">gabriell context(e\'s answers about Abuse Survivors)</a></li>\r\n	<li>my pretty strong scientific-psychological spirit characters <a title="Sci + Psy, Go There" href="http://daresayGoThere.quora.com">Sci + Psy Z<em> daresay Go There</em></a></li>\r\n	<li>trans* / youth empowerment, homelessness (I ask questions, like <a title="Homelessness: What is more sensitive and attentive wording than &quot;homeless&quot; and &quot;homeless shelter?&quot;" href="http://www.quora.com/Homelessness/What-is-more-sensitive-and-attentive-wording-than-homeless-and-homeless-shelter">Homelessness: What is more sensitive and attentive wording than "homeless" and "homeless shelter?"</a>)</li>\r\n	<li>also i\'ll write about why i\'m banned from Quora right now for my grammar "style", talking like i think.. right.</li>\r\n	<li>more very soon, as I am finally beginning to organize it all-and-not-and-maybe together.</li>\r\n	<li>have a lil fun searching around while I keep organizing :) it will come together...</li>\r\n	<li>maybe start with my video(s) or poems...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\nReality is, til True is still growing —|—|—|—|——|—|—|——|—|—|—i\r\n\r\nIt helps Sci + Psy Z et al is ALL FREE, Public Domain and Creative Commons :)\r\n\r\n<iframe width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLtGcG1ERBHdSKOTW3Eth3Mhc3aMKY8PHL"></iframe>\r\n\r\nWelcoming all feedback. Share what you feel and think by replying to public ideas and links, as much as you like, as often as you like, for as long as you like, especially if it helps <em>go there.</em>\r\n\r\nEmail <a title="lilbigfeelthinkheartmindshieldscipsyreali@tilTrue.com" href="mailto:lilbigfeelthinkheartmindshieldscipsyreali@tilTrue.com">lilbigfeelthinkheartmindshieldscipsyreali@tilTrue.com</a>. Feel free and think free to email as much as you like, as often as you like, for as long as you like, especially if it helps <em>go there.</em>\r\n\r\ni am also @\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title="facebook: prosody" href="http://fb.com/prosody">fb.com/prosody</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="YouTube: Silence Silence, Missing Heart and Mind: Shhh-Lost-and-Profound (Video Playlist | Spoken Word)" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J8gnbv9jbZY&amp;list=PLtGcG1ERBHdSKOTW3Eth3Mhc3aMKY8PHL">Silence Silence, Missing Heart and Mind: Shhh-Lost-and-Profound (Spoken Word)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="facebook: prosody" href="http://quora.com/Gabriell-Gaston-Croft">gabriell\'s Quora About Me</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="Twitter / frets" href="http://twitter.com/frets">twitter.com/frets</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="G+" href="http://gplus.to/context">gplus.to/context</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="LinkedIn" href="http://linkedin.com/in/gabriellcontext">linkedin.com/in/gabriellcontext</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="YouTube" href="http://youtube.com/iGabe">Gabriell\'s YouTube</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="/assets/3q8dzg.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-43" title="Psy Z Hundredthoughts" alt="Psy Z Hundredthoughts: Heart, Shield and Mind." src="http://tiltrue.com/assets/3q8dzg.jpg" width="625" height="407" /></a>', 'til True', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed